1
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,490
♪Memories rise like towers so high♪

2
00:00:21,780 --> 00:00:24,760
♪Promises now seem ugly and dry♪

3
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:28,180
♪Time devours like a wild beast♪

4
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:31,090
♪It locks its gaze right onto me♪

5
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:35,160
♪You're the one who knows how to let go♪

6
00:00:35,480 --> 00:00:38,630
♪You always leave, like the show♪

7
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:41,500
♪I envy how you come and go♪

8
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:44,440
♪For you, letting go is easy♪

9
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:47,500
♪You tore right through my heart♪

10
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:51,740
♪You turned away from my tears♪

11
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:54,120
♪The story shatters into pieces♪

12
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:56,920
♪All that's left is emptiness♪

13
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:59,150
♪How am I supposed to carry on?♪

14
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,190
♪You break the night like the dawn♪

15
00:01:01,190 --> 00:01:05,810
♪Leaving me lost in the deep♪

16
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:09,250
♪Love is just an illusion♪

17
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:12,400
♪Like a dream that I couldn't keep♪

18
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:20,220
=Paramount=

19
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:23,220
=Episode 23=

20
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:31,940
Why did you tell me all this?

21
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:39,260
Let's work together

22
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:42,650
to take down Qian Muchen.

23
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:46,780
Deal.

24
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:16,850
The gunshots alerted others.

25
00:02:17,170 --> 00:02:18,170
It's not safe here.

26
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:19,970
We need to go. Now.

27
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:27,300
♪You say you can't give me what I want♪

28
00:02:30,890 --> 00:02:31,770
Please come again.

29
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:34,220
Take care.

30
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:36,900
My Lady, hurry and get in.

31
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:46,020
♪But you never walked toward me again♪

32
00:02:47,090 --> 00:02:47,940
I want to look around.

33
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,260
Aren't you my guide?

34
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:55,420
♪Lost my courage to reach for you♪

35
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:59,050
♪I'm returning the loneliness we shared♪

36
00:02:59,090 --> 00:02:59,930
To where?

37
00:03:01,210 --> 00:03:02,050
Get in the car.

38
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:05,890
It hasn't been washed.

39
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:11,410
♪There's not a hint of regret
in your eyes♪

40
00:03:11,450 --> 00:03:12,290
Now it's clean.

41
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:13,910
I really admire you.

42
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:20,220
♪I shouldn't have come into your life♪

43
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,450
Mr. Luo, it's pretty late.

44
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:44,100
Something urgent?

45
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,130
Come to think of it,

46
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:48,930
we've never really talked one-on-one.

47
00:03:53,010 --> 00:03:53,850
True.

48
00:03:55,530 --> 00:03:56,420
I came to tell you

49
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:57,420
a lead about Caishen.

50
00:03:59,530 --> 00:04:00,450
Lately,

51
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,820
Paramount has been

52
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,010
receiving Caishen's goods.

53
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:06,270
When your warehouse
was burned down,

54
00:04:09,980 --> 00:04:10,820
I was there.

55
00:04:12,290 --> 00:04:13,130
What?

56
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:14,540
That night,

57
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:16,730
I was following Caishen

58
00:04:17,890 --> 00:04:19,010
to your warehouse.

59
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:23,370
What do you mean?

60
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:26,700
I think

61
00:04:27,810 --> 00:04:29,980
Caishen might have worked at Paramount.

62
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:36,890
Why are you looking for Caishen?

63
00:04:42,450 --> 00:04:43,450
I'm trying to help Luo.

64
00:04:56,810 --> 00:04:58,370
I can help you find Caishen.

65
00:05:01,620 --> 00:05:02,730
Take good care of Luo.

66
00:05:07,170 --> 00:05:08,450
She's already left the Dock Gang.

67
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,340
Qian Muchen.

68
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:27,700
If you care about Luo,

69
00:05:28,290 --> 00:05:29,130
show some courage.

70
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:30,900
She really needs you.

71
00:05:32,220 --> 00:05:33,160
I'm heading out first.

72
00:05:35,530 --> 00:05:36,700
Why are you telling me this?

73
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:39,010
Don't you care about Luo too?

74
00:05:50,810 --> 00:05:51,650
What do you think

75
00:05:52,090 --> 00:05:52,930
love really is?

76
00:05:54,930 --> 00:05:55,770
My love

77
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:57,980
means sacrifice.

78
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:25,420
What brings you here?

79
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:36,810
Luo Shi told me
you left the Dock Gang.

80
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:39,890
Luo, come back.

81
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:42,420
Let's find Caishen together.

82
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:51,770
But I don't want to use you anymore.

83
00:06:57,740 --> 00:06:58,930
I'm about to leave Lin City.

84
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:04,450
What?

85
00:07:05,090 --> 00:07:06,420
This is the Bai family's property.

86
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:08,770
I've bought it.

87
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:10,770
I'm giving it back.

88
00:07:22,810 --> 00:07:23,650
Why did you do this?

89
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:32,330
I'm not asking for your forgiveness.

90
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,650
I just want to do more for you

91
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,420
before I leave.

92
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:39,460
Luo Shi once asked me,

93
00:07:40,610 --> 00:07:41,450
what is love?

94
00:07:49,490 --> 00:07:50,660
For me, it means letting go.

95
00:07:54,330 --> 00:07:55,170
Something happened.

96
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:56,490
Mr. Qian...

97
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,020
He's gone.

98
00:07:59,140 --> 00:07:59,980
What?

99
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,770
Someone broke into Qian Residence

100
00:08:02,050 --> 00:08:03,050
and hurt him.

101
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:04,580
We're still checking

102
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:05,580
the exact time of death.

103
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:08,820
Oh, right,

104
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,580
when we checked the body,

105
00:08:10,810 --> 00:08:12,210
we found this in Mr. Qian's jacket.

106
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:16,740
You can head out now.

107
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,700
Yes.

108
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:46,930
This might lead us to

109
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:48,210
his deepest secrets.

110
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:01,700
(Qizhi Girls' School Student File:
Zhao Lingchun)

111
00:09:08,490 --> 00:09:09,700
Remember this watch?

112
00:09:10,020 --> 00:09:10,960
It belonged to Caishen.

113
00:09:16,490 --> 00:09:17,330
Look at this person.

114
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,650
His birthmark

115
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:20,900
is just like Caishen's symbol.

116
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:23,140
Zhang Fu'an.

117
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,900
He might be the hitman
Qian Zhongli sent.

118
00:09:30,210 --> 00:09:31,900
He grew up in Lin'an Welfare Home.

119
00:09:36,700 --> 00:09:38,500
(Lin'an Welfare Home)

120
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:42,420
Young Master,

121
00:09:43,370 --> 00:09:44,370
Lin Na is in trouble.

122
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:54,770
I need to go.

123
00:09:57,290 --> 00:09:58,130
It's alright.

124
00:09:58,540 --> 00:09:59,810
I can handle it on my own.

125
00:10:00,260 --> 00:10:01,510
Going to the welfare home alone?

126
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:02,980
I'm a bit worried.

127
00:10:08,730 --> 00:10:09,570
Go ahead.

128
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:11,060
I'll look after Luo.

129
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:12,500
With me here,

130
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:13,700
she'll be safe.

131
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:28,300
(East Asia Hotel)

132
00:10:58,260 --> 00:10:59,100
Qing'an.

133
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:00,980
Mr. Qian.

134
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:02,180
Long time no see.

135
00:11:02,490 --> 00:11:03,490
Who are you really?

136
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:06,060
Weren't you all

137
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:07,660
looking for me this whole time?

138
00:11:11,490 --> 00:11:12,580
You're Caishen.

139
00:11:18,050 --> 00:11:19,260
Correct.

140
00:11:44,620 --> 00:11:50,540
♪I can pretend like nothing's wrong♪

141
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:57,420
♪You say you can't give me what I want♪

142
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:03,180
♪But what did I ever ask for♪

143
00:12:03,820 --> 00:12:07,900
♪Just having you feels like a luxury♪

144
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:11,660
♪The love you gave was never enough♪

145
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:13,860
♪To keep me warm inside♪

146
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:20,580
♪Should I be glad
I saw the cracks so soon?♪

147
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:24,820
♪But how do I fix the hole in my soul?♪

148
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:28,580
♪You found a thousand excuses♪

149
00:12:28,580 --> 00:12:31,660
♪Just to make me hurt more♪

150
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:35,580
♪I reached out—
hoping you'd take my hand♪

151
00:12:35,580 --> 00:12:37,180
♪But you stepped back once again♪

152
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:43,500
♪Back to where our first encounter began♪

153
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:49,260
♪But you never walked toward me again♪

154
00:12:50,060 --> 00:12:54,420
♪I erased your name from my mind♪

155
00:12:54,420 --> 00:12:58,660
♪Lost my courage to reach for you♪

156
00:12:58,860 --> 00:13:02,740
♪I'm returning the loneliness we shared♪

157
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:06,900
♪Still gasping from a hurt
too much to bear♪

158
00:13:07,140 --> 00:13:10,940
♪Your calm makes the whole room heavy♪

159
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:14,940
♪There's not a hint of regret
in your eyes♪

160
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:22,100
♪Maybe I never belonged in your life♪
